A Nigerian socio-political activist, Aisha Yesufu has reacted to the comment made by the Senior Special Adviser to President Muhammadu Buhari on Media and Publicity, Garba Shehu. DAILY POST reports that the president’s spokesman on Friday declared that nobody can bring down the Buhari-led Government, stressing that his principal was democratically elected. Garba Shehu made the assertion when he featured on the Channels TV programme, Sunrise Daily. Reacting, Aisha Yesufu in a tweet on her verified Twitter handle on Saturday, said “you cannot bring down what is already down”. According to her, the government only needs to go up. Her tweet reads: “Spokesperson to the President, Garba Shehu @GarShehu said nobody can bring Buhari’s govt down and I agree with him. “You cannot bring down what is already down. We are making demands to bring the government up and doing”.